<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - ERROR GOBLOK</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/logo.png">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Mono:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body, html {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #2a2a2a 0%, #000000 100%);
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noiseFilter'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.65' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noiseFilter)' opacity='0.05'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 40px;
            border: 3px solid #ff0000;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 85%;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);
            position: relative;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 100px;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #fff;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
            position: relative;
            text-shadow: 4px 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8), -4px 0 rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.8);
            line-height: 1;
        }
        
        h1::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 50%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 5px;
            background: #ff0000;
            transform: skewY(-5deg);
        }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 28px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #ff0000;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            line-height: 1.3;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        p {
            color: #cccccc;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            border-left: 2px solid #555;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #ff0000;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 3px solid #ff0000;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff0000;
            color: #000;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 0px #ffffff;
        }

        .btn:active {
            transform: translate(2px, 2px);
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 25px;
                width: 85%;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 60px;
                letter-spacing: -2px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 20px;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 14px;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                padding: 12px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 380px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 48px;
            }
            
            h2 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>NYASAR, GOBLOK, TOLOL LU PALA E GEDE LU KONTOL!</h2>
        <p>
            Ngapain lo di sini? Udah jelas nggak ada apa-apa. <br>
            Mata lo burem atau tangan lo yang nggak becus ngetik URL? <br>
            Buang-buang resource server gue aja.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">BALIK SANA, CEPETAN!</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>